{"tid":1355384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說:醒下啦！  試着說:返嚟啦！","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:58:09.000Z","uid":176699,"like":201,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"1c748ac68e3ad42f53095c78733761975d19237c","tid":1355384,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"呢排大家情緒其實都好低落，大家都好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n其實2-3小時嘅休息真係好緊要<br />\n<br />\n見到大家都成日叫人醒下啦，對準政權<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我並唔反對，兼且同意</span><br />\n<br />\n不過呢d說話好消極<br />\n<br />\n冇人當義士係condom，亦冇人分散注意力，其實依家所有發生嘅事都係反送中做源頭<br />\n<br />\n香港太多問題今次一次過爆曬出嚟，所以睇落好似唔集中<br />\n但我地最終目的都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對付中共大魔頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說:醒下啦！  試着說:返嚟啦！繼續做正經野啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61af4c5aa5dfe1b87a2fc935897f68b9b9e21f3d","tid":1355384,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c47a9660a735844fb0b4937739bd9e839d1fca8","tid":1355384,"uid":81934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:50:28.000Z","msg":"[緊急置頂] 724癱瘓地鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8430ac93c79f821802bc197f5b10911d294acac","tid":1355384,"uid":176699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"我地要正面能量推多d人一齊行落去"},{"pid":"30794370b588be2f08bf1786afefc65dd6258509","tid":1355384,"uid":176699,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗下下笑下都起曬鋼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">唔好唔記得日本點解冇人搞社運</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f53a6d6cec0133f1a134fbe55d3e9a93dbd3c96","tid":1355384,"uid":1766